From 47cdc9de76105cd0f95ed2a07616949da029c437 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Takagi Tasuku <tasuren@outlook.jp>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 12:31:51 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 13/40] Add per-session token handshake for IPC authentication

Introduce a session token that must be verified before any Mojo API
call is accepted:

- cbf_browser.mojom: add Authenticate(string token) => (bool ok) as
  the first method of CbfBrowserService.
- CbfBrowserService: accept session token in constructor; gate all
  methods behind authenticated_ flag; implement Authenticate().
- cbf_bridge_auth.cc: implement CbfBridgeClient::Authenticate() which
  calls browser_remote_->Authenticate(), then sets up BrowserObserver
  and SetObserver() on success; expose cbf_bridge_client_authenticate.
---
